---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 24, 2026";
---

<Layout 
  title="Disclaimer - Upraizo"
  description="Upraizo Disclaimer. Read our policies regarding results, expectations, and the educational nature of our content."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/30 border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-t-3xl">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Legal & Compliance</h2>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Disclaimer
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-medium">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-16 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">1. Educational Purposes Only</h2>
          <p>
            The information, courses, and resources provided by Upraizo are for educational and informational purposes only. While our master mentors share their experiences and proven frameworks, nothing on this website should be construed as professional, legal, financial, or psychological advice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">2. No Guarantee of Results</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We are dedicated to providing high-quality soft skills and leadership training. However, <strong>we do not make any guarantees about your ability to get results, earn more money, get a promotion, or achieve any specific outcome</strong> using our ideas, tools, or strategies.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your success depends entirely on your own effort, motivation, commitment, and follow-through. You alone are responsible and accountable for your decisions, actions, and results in life and business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">3. Testimonials and Examples</h2>
          <p>
            Any testimonials, case studies, or examples shown on the Upraizo website are exceptional results and do not reflect the typical purchaser's experience. They are not intended to represent or guarantee that anyone will achieve the same or similar results. 
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/20 border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-900/30">
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 mb-6 tracking-tight">4. "As Is" Basis</h2>
          <p class="text-indigo-800 dark:text-indigo-200">
            All content and services on our platform are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranties of any kind, either express or implied. Upraizo makes no representations or warranties in relation to the accuracy or completeness of the information found on it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">5. External Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our courses and website may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by us. We do not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any information on these external websites.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">6. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or require more information about our site's disclaimer, please feel free to contact us by email at:
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:support@upraizo.com" class="inline-flex mt-6 px-8 py-4 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-zinc-900 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
            support@upraizo.com
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
